     * Overview
     * Details

   EXCLUSIVE FOR M·A·C SELECT MEMBERS
   No Rating

Prep+Prime Fix+ (Shimmer)

   EXCLUSIVE FOR M·A·C SELECT MEMBERS

A Fix+ formula now infused with pearlescent pearls for the ultimate glow.

   R 355.00
   100 ml
     * Pinklite
     * Goldlite

   (BUTTON) (BUTTON)

Full Description

   Fan-favourite Fix+ is now infused with pearlescent particles for the
   ultimate glow. This formula still carries all the hydrating, soothing
   and refreshing benefits of the original version and improves the wear
   of makeup up to 12 hours, along with the addition of pearl for an
   ultra-illuminating effect on skin. Skin looks both healthy and radiant.

Key Claims and Benefits

   Immediately illuminates and adds radianceProvides instant and long-term
   hydrationImproves and extends the wear of makeup up to 12
   hoursConditions skinHelps to set and prolong the wear of makeupFor all
   skin typesOphthalmologist testedDermatologist testedNon-acnegenic

Usage

   Shake well to disperse pearlescent particles before each use.Hold
   bottle eight to twelve inches away from face and mist directly onto
   skin, while keeping eyes and mouth closed.Spray before makeup to create
   a dewy canvas.Spray over makeup for an ultra-natural makeup
   look.Rehydrate makeup throughout the day to freshen your look and
   enhance its finish.

Ingredients

