   EXCLUSIVE FOR M·A·C SELECT MEMBERS
   No Rating

Prep+Prime Fix+ Mattifying Mist

   EXCLUSIVE FOR M·A·C SELECT MEMBERS
   R 355.00
   100 ml

Full Description

   A lightweight mattifying spray that refreshes skin while instantly
   controlling shine and oil on the surface without disturbing makeup. The
   innovative formula contains powders, silica and other oil-absorbing
   agents to help set makeup, rebalance and mattify skin.

