     * Prep+Prime Fix+ / Mini M·A·C

     * Overview
     * Details

   EXCLUSIVE FOR M·A·C SELECT MEMBERS
   No Rating

Prep+Prime Fix+ / Mini M·A·C

   EXCLUSIVE FOR M·A·C SELECT MEMBERS

A mini lightweight water mist that refreshes skin and finishes makeup.
Discounts do not apply.

   R 195.00
   30 ml

Full Description

   An aqua-spritz of vitamin and minerals, infused with a calm-the-skin
   blend of green tea, chamomile, cucumber, topped off with the fresh,
   natural, energizing scent of Sugi. Adds radiance, finishes makeup.
   Spray it on. Skin drinks it up! Pro discount is not applicable.

Key Claims and Benefits

     * Soothes and refreshes skin
     * Hydrating
     * Dermatologist tested
     * Ophthalmologist tested
     * Non-acnegenic

Usage

     * Hold bottle 12 inches away from face and spray evenly.
     * Use alone or to finish makeup.

Ingredients

